Extract it to your desktop then go to your desktop and click runserver.To get on the server load up moparscape and just click log in and make up a user name and pass , don’t change the ip.For other people to join go to

www.hamachi.cc

and download hamachi and make a new netowrk and tell people your network name and pass so they an join it.How would they join it? They would take the adress beside your name on hamachi and run moparscape and got o file newserver and paste that ip in there and log in with a made up user name and pass.
